OL,3,CCriminals being freed from jail early
OL,4,Cto cut overcrowding
OL,6,FCriminals including a domestic abuser
OL,7,Fwho posed a risk to children have been
OL,8,Ffreed from jail early as part of a
OL,9,FGovernment bid to cut overcrowding, a
OL,10,Fwatchdog has warned.
OL,12,FChief inspector of prisons Charlie
OL,13,FTaylor raised "serious concerns" about
OL,14,Fthe policy as he highlighted examples
OL,15,Fof high-risk inmates selected for
OL,16,Fearly release.
