OL,3,CCriminals being freed from jail early
OL,4,Cto cut overcrowding
OL,6,FFirst announced last year, the
OL,7,FGovernment insisted the measure would
OL,8,Fbe temporary and would only allow "low-
OL,9,Flevel offenders" out of prison up to
OL,10,F18 days early under strict supervision.
OL,12,FBut earlier this month Mr Taylor
OL,13,Fdescribed the prison system as
OL,14,F"creaking at every level" as it
OL,15,Femerged ministers were preparing to
OL,16,Fextend the scheme for a second time so
OL,17,Fsome criminals could be freed from
OL,18,Fjail up to 70 days before their
OL,19,Frelease date.
