OL,3,CCriminals being freed from jail early
OL,4,Cto cut overcrowding
OL,6,FIn a report published on Tuesday, Mr
OL,7,FTaylor said a "high-risk" inmate at
OL,8,FHMP Lewes in East Sussex, who posed a
OL,9,Fdanger to children, had his release
OL,10,Fdate brought forward despite "having a
OL,11,Fhistory of stalking, domestic abuse
OL,12,Fand being subject to a restraining
OL,13,Forder".
