OL,3,CCriminals being freed from jail early
OL,4,Cto cut overcrowding
OL,6,FThe watchdog's concerns came to light
OL,7,Fin findings from an inspection at the
OL,8,FEast Sussex jail carried out in
OL,9,FFebruary, shortly after the scheme was
OL,10,Fbrought into force. Inspectors
OL,11,Funcovered major problems with drugs,
OL,12,Fviolence and self-harm at the category
OL,13,FB Victorian prison, the report said.
OL,15,FMr Taylor found the way the policy was
OL,16,Fbeing put into action was
OL,17,F"undermining" safe releases of
OL,18,Fprisoners.
