OL,3,CCriminals being freed from jail early
OL,4,Cto cut overcrowding
OL,6,FRelease dates for some high-risk
OL,7,Fprisoners had been "brought forward at
OL,8,Fshort notice, forcing already
OL,9,Fstretched resettlement agencies to
OL,10,Fredraw existing plans from scratch in
OL,11,Fas little as two or three weeks",
OL,12,Faccording to the report.
OL,14,FThe need to release offenders early to
OL,15,Ffree up space in jails is another sign
OL,16,Fof the pressure prisons are under, Mr
OL,17,FTaylor said as he branded the
OL,18,Fsituation "entirely predictable" and
OL,19,F"simply not sustainable".
