OL,3,CCriminals being freed from jail early
OL,4,Cto cut overcrowding
OL,6,FLabour's shadow justice secretary
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood accused the Government
OL,8,Fof a "cover-up" over its early release
OL,9,Fscheme and said: "The public will
OL,10,Frightly be worried to hear of cases
OL,11,Fwhere violent prisoners are being
OL,12,Freleased without a proper assessment
OL,13,Fof the risk they pose to the public,
OL,14,Fand specifically children.
OL,16,F"It's being left to prison inspectors
OL,17,Fto tell the public the truth because
OL,18,Fthis Government is refusing to level
OL,19,Fwith them on the scale of the prisons
OL,20,Fand probation crisis."
