OL,6,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk
OL,7,Fpreviously came under fire amid
OL,8,Faccusations of a lack of transparency
OL,9,Fabout the plans.
OL,11,FAndrea Coomber, chief executive of
OL,12,Fcharity the Howard League for Penal
OL,13,FReform, said: "It is imperative that
OL,14,Fthe Government publishes data on the
OL,15,Fearly release scheme's operation and
OL,16,Fmakes a commitment to transparency as
OL,17,Fa matter of urgency.
