OL,3,CCriminals being freed from jail early
OL,4,Cto cut overcrowding
OL,6,F"While action to ease pressure on
OL,7,Fjails is necessary, this temporary
OL,8,Fmeasure is no substitute for what is
OL,9,Freally needed: a more sensible
OL,10,Fresponse to crime that puts fewer
OL,11,Fpeople behind bars and more money into
OL,12,Fservices that can help them."
OL,14,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "While we will always ensure
OL,16,Fthere is enough capacity to keep
OL,17,Fdangerous offenders behind bars, this
OL,18,Fscheme allows us to ease short-term
OL,19,Fpressures on prisons by moving some
OL,20,Flower-level offenders at the end of
OL,21,Ftheir custodial term on to licence.
